      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SPARKLING WHEELS (2) has been in sparkling form recording back to back wins, the latest at this track last time over 400m in (22.74). Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Ideally placed to take this out. SHY HI (4) hasn't been far away here at the last two, finding the frame both times, most recently when second beaten 6 lengths (23.00). Has a win and six places times at this track. Good beginner but will need a little luck from a middle draw. Expected to be in this for a long way. GARY INDIANA (1) racing well without winning, placing at his last four runs. Last time finished 3rd in a Grade 5 on May 30 over 400m at this track behind Savina beaten 4 lengths (23.45). Some good form is emerging from his last run. Likely to be in the finish again. RITZA ROCKER (7) must be respected as a past winner at this course and distance.",
